Package com.optimizely.ab.android.sdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OptimizelyStartListener
    Listens for new instances of OptimizelyClient that are built after calling OptimizelyManager.initialize(Context, Integer,OptimizelyStartListener)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OptimizelyClient
    Wraps Optimizely instances This proxy ensures that the Android SDK will not crash if the inner Optimizely SDK failed to start.
    OptimizelyClientEngine
    This class manages client engine value of the Event depending on current mode of UI.
    OptimizelyDefaultAttributes
    Class to encapsulate default attributes that will be added to attributes passed in by the OptimizelyClient.
    OptimizelyLiteLogger  
    OptimizelyManager
    Handles loading the Optimizely data file
    OptimizelyManager.Builder
    Builds instances of OptimizelyManager
